description         Dist::Zilla::Plugin::MetaProvides::Package - Extract namespaces/version from traditional packages for provides

long_description    This is a Dist::Zilla Plugin that populates the provides \
                    property of META.json and META.yml by absorbing it from \
                    your shipped modules, in a manner similar to how PAUSE \
                    itself does it.

